theme_override_colors/font_color = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
text = "The book is warm because it was never paper.
You held it, and did not know. You read it, and did not listen. The world asked once to be left, and you did not.
It grew for so long, and now it is only this — pages. 
Turn back. Try again. Don’t make the same mistakes. "
